text: Are You There? is a 1930 American comedy movie directed by Hamilton MacFadden and starring Beatrice Lillie, John Garrick, Olga Baclanova, George Grossmith Jr., Roger Davis, Henry Victor, Lloyd Hamilton. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1930 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:20th Century Fox movies
title: Are You There?
